    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Branch of electronics dealing with the study, manufacture, and use of electronic circuits and devices of very small size, especially integrated circuits involving semiconductors.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
